Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.30,0:00:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相聚一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.60,0:00:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翌晨的陽光就快來臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.74,0:00:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照進這間充滿煙蒂\N雜亂無章的屋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.79,0:00:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Tell me why 聖母瑪利亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.72,0:00:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我對溫柔感到飢渴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.89,0:00:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Tell me why
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.63,0:00:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼孤單的夜晚\N總是如此漫長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.54,0:00:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牛仔褲下的膝蓋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.34,0:00:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被破碎的夢想打溼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.71,0:01:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿著襯衫的胸部太過耀眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.72,0:01:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜歡妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.25,0:01:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這陣子真的很感謝妳的照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.52,0:01:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別客氣,千萬別這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.72,0:01:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.06,0:01:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您明天就要回去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.72,0:01:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是遺憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.82,0:01:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再多待幾天有什麼關係呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.43,0:01:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也想多待幾天\N可是要準備過孟蘭節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.76,0:01:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我老伴一年才回來這麼一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.93,0:01:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不在家的話\N他一定會很寂寞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.84,0:02:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.44,0:02:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且這傢伙現在身處的狀況\N我也很了解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.92,0:02:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這話什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.28,0:02:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就如妳看到的\N雖然他是個靠不住的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.52,0:02:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還請妳多多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.39,0:02:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.39,0:02:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.86,0:02:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪裡,別這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.96,0:02:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,你也磕頭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.89,0:02:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.17,0:02:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#70再見了,奶奶!\N上野車站陷入宴會混亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.05,0:02:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.92,0:02:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裕作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.32,0:02:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回來的時候去幫我買\N新幹線的對號車票還有土產
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.39,0:02:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.09,0:02:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要搞丟了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.53,0:02:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,土產要買什麼好呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.30,0:02:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要是東京的東西,什麼都好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.40,0:03:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.07,0:03:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.07,0:03:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.71,0:03:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳要回鄉下啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.24,0:03:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.81,0:03:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您要回去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.81,0:03:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您不是打算永遠住在這裡嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.62,0:03:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找的零錢不要私吞喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.79,0:03:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你們的照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.02,0:03:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳走了我會很寂寞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.66,0:03:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今晚得盛大的喝個痛快才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.66,0:03:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思,還讓你這麼費心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.10,0:03:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.93,0:03:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.97,0:03:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.37,0:03:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你今天也要整天都去面試嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.24,0:03:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會,今天只去一家公司而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.68,0:03:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那太好了,結束以後\N陪我上街買東西好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.91,0:03:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.35,0:03:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想買個禮物送給奶奶\N謝謝她的照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.29,0:03:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用這麼多禮啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.76,0:03:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼,只是一點心意而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.72,0:04:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊,我想12點就會結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.66,0:04:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我再打電話給妳,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.83,0:04:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請好好加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.57,0:05:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.84,0:05:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你覺得送這個給奶奶怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.74,0:05:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得很好啊,不過太浪費了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.15,0:05:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起喔,我一直無法決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.85,0:05:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.15,0:05:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我再去看一看,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.25,0:05:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳慢慢看沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.07,0:05:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最便宜的也要30萬啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.68,0:05:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先生您在找訂婚戒指嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.84,0:05:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,不是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.08,0:06:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,訂婚戒指的價位\N大多都是薪水三個月份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.72,0:06:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一帶的,您覺得如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.85,0:06:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,我是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.72,0:06:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.56,0:06:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.33,0:06:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.96,0:06:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.13,0:06:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.00,0:06:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出了什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.13,0:06:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.55,0:06:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,訂婚戒指的價位\N大多都是薪水三個月份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.26,0:06:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.02,0:06:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.33,0:06:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員,我跟妳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.83,0:06:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.36,0:06:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定會找到工作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.27,0:06:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.56,0:07:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也要喝嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.24,0:07:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好喝嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.89,0:07:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員人那麼好\N養的狗卻這麼厚臉皮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.06,0:07:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我精心釀造的梅子酒耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.06,0:07:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心存感激的喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.25,0:08:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你酒量蠻好的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.96,0:08:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不好意思,全部都讓你拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.23,0:08:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.90,0:08:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.27,0:08:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.94,0:08:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天真的很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.27,0:08:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能夠跟妳單獨上街購物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.74,0:08:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對喔,這好像是第一次呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.38,0:08:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像要下雨了,快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.55,0:08:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.60,0:09:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.90,0:09:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.70,0:09:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,惣一郎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.38,0:09:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有酒臭味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.44,0:09:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酒臭味?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.91,0:09:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶,妳幹了什麼好事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.31,0:09:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.65,0:09:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要這樣,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.82,0:09:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這隻笨狗在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.69,0:09:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不快住手,放開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.76,0:09:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在搞什麼啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.86,0:09:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員,已經沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.52,0:10:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶的告別…不對,送別會開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.82,0:10:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不好意思\N還為我舉辦送別會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.66,0:10:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裕作,你要鬧彆扭到什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.63,0:10:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.63,0:10:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的,這孩子真拿他沒輒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.80,0:10:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,習慣就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.13,0:10:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,剛才…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.64,0:10:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係,可是我不是故意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.07,0:10:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.74,0:10:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.75,0:10:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.12,0:10:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每個人輪流說幾句話\N送給奶奶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.16,0:10:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.16,0:10:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該說什麼好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.43,0:10:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我爺爺奶奶\N在我小時候就過世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.33,0:10:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到您才知道\N原來奶奶是這種感覺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.70,0:10:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好嚴肅喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.07,0:10:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然,別期待管理員會說笑話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.94,0:10:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.41,0:10:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是一點小禮物\N謝謝您的照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.85,0:10:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請您收下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.88,0:11:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以打開來看嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.51,0:11:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.82,0:11:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很不錯耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.22,0:11:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好酷喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.12,0:11:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果您能喜歡,我就很高興了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.26,0:11:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員真是個好人,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.46,0:11:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼\N朱美,輪到妳說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.27,0:11:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望妳很快再回來坐坐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.24,0:11:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女人的一生是不滅的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.77,0:11:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再創造另一次高峰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.54,0:11:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼,輪到我說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.04,0:11:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煮木栖菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.38,0:11:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬鈴薯燉肉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.18,0:11:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,炒牛蒡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.45,0:11:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鴨肉炒茄子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.92,0:11:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什錦壽司飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.99,0:11:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在說什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.99,0:11:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他每天都來討奶奶做的飯吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.72,0:11:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是好吃極了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.59,0:11:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請務必再來做給我吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.70,0:11:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你們,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.41,0:12:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.84,0:12:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不小心就喝太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.38,0:12:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好漂亮喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.39,0:12:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停電了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.25,0:12:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蠟燭,快拿蠟燭來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.59,0:12:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷好像打在這附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.12,0:12:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別…別害怕,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.26,0:12:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有我保護妳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.43,0:12:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牠什麼時候?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.97,0:12:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-走開啦,不要這樣\N-不要這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.74,0:12:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.84,0:12:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎,不要這樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.54,0:12:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙的酒還沒醒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.51,0:12:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要舔了,噁心死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.78,0:12:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎,過來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.69,0:12:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好乖,好乖\N來,喝一杯安靜下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.56,0:12:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶,不能再讓牠喝了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.03,0:12:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是狗,牠也會感到寂寞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.76,0:12:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一起喝到雨停吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.23,0:13:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎真是傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.84,0:13:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牠一直黏著妳耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.84,0:13:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這實在很反常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.11,0:13:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來牠真的很愛管理員啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.31,0:13:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在鬧什麼彆扭?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.31,0:13:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.45,0:13:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,狗跟人是一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.12,0:13:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也會想向喜歡的人撒嬌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.39,0:13:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也別認輸,過去撒嬌不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.59,0:13:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少囉嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.49,0:14:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎喲,少爺,不要發火嘛\N來一杯怎麼樣啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.80,0:14:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎,再喝一杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.43,0:14:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶,不要再讓牠…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.97,0:14:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然俗話說什麼人養什麼狗\N可是這隻狗卻一點都不像妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.78,0:14:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員的老公,酒品也很差嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.71,0:14:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對喔,惣一郎原本是\N妳老公養的狗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.95,0:14:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才不會呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.28,0:14:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我老公根本不會喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.35,0:14:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且他是個認真自律的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.29,0:14:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會這樣死纏著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.43,0:14:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來他是個好老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.93,0:14:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.04,0:14:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像這樣躺在大腿上\N好像一對夫妻喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.28,0:14:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎,我們下樓去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.55,0:14:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧,親愛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.12,0:14:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.29,0:15:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能兩人單獨相處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.69,0:15:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,快走開啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.56,0:15:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.16,0:15:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他喝醉酒都是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.27,0:15:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.81,0:15:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打吧,打吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.48,0:15:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.53,0:15:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.24,0:15:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裕作,我要走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.94,0:15:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經快一點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.88,0:16:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我宿醉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.15,0:16:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那又怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.58,0:16:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不用去找工作嗎?\N不幫我拿行李去車站嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.29,0:16:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我能幫妳拿行李\N我早就出去找工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.33,0:16:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是沒用的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.54,0:16:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要乖乖的喔,我會再來看你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.81,0:16:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裕作,你在幹什麼!快一點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.78,0:16:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真沒用,才喝那麼點酒就不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.55,0:16:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看,惣一郎的精神好得很呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.09,0:16:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.26,0:16:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也送您去車站吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.69,0:16:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊,真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.10,0:16:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不要緊吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.50,0:16:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行李我來拿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.07,0:16:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用了,我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.94,0:16:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.77,0:17:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.07,0:17:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差兩歲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.65,0:17:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶,等一下喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.25,0:17:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們大家一起去送妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.90,0:17:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見了,奶奶,妳要多保重喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.26,0:17:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再拿梅子酒來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.43,0:17:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶,妳真的要再來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.90,0:17:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,謝謝你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.91,0:17:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真抱歉,還讓你們送到車站來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.28,0:17:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.65,0:17:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真抱歉,還讓你們跟著來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.59,0:17:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為五代那個樣子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.35,0:17:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,實在太丟臉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.36,0:17:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裝作不認識他好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.50,0:17:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,你不要緊吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.50,0:18:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對…對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.89,0:18:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到到最後\N我孫子還是給你們添了麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.49,0:18:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們已經習慣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.66,0:18:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裕作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.00,0:18:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三餐一定要按時吃喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.97,0:18:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有,找到工作要馬上通知我\N知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.37,0:18:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,妳要小心點喔,奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.32,0:19:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,19號月台,由上野發車\N開往新瀉的特快車要開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.26,0:19:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,送行的人請退到白線後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.44,0:19:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才在高崎附近發生線路意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.91,0:19:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很抱歉耽誤各位旅客的時間\N請稍候片刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.49,0:19:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真抱歉,還讓你們陪我一起等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.33,0:19:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正我們也閒閒沒事幹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.90,0:19:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說還不知道何時會恢復通車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.97,0:19:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.00,0:19:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好想早點回去睡覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.64,0:19:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我買啤酒來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.78,0:19:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐在這裡發呆也沒用嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.48,0:19:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.01,0:19:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乾杯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.88,0:19:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家盡量喝,盡量喝!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.09,0:20:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是稀奇,你竟然宿醉得這麼厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.39,0:20:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,一起來喝歡送酒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.09,0:20:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…不必了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.43,0:20:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,你們不可以這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.90,0:20:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼關係,反正閒著也是閒著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.34,0:20:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要一起來喝一杯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.77,0:20:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裝作不認識,裝作不認識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.31,0:20:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,你要去哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.55,0:20:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酒的味道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.45,0:20:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要去遠一點的地方透透氣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.62,0:20:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員,你們要去哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.79,0:20:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶,妳看\N那是五代最拿手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.43,0:20:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假裝喝醉抱得緊緊的,好噁心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.74,0:20:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙太不像話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.27,0:20:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別想逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.00,0:20:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逮捕你們喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.55,0:20:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.89,0:21:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓各位久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.56,0:21:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,19號月台,由上野發車\N開往新瀉的特快車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.63,0:21:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備要開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.93,0:21:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說管理員啊\N妳就死心來跟我們一起喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.06,0:21:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要跟我講喝酒的事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.67,0:21:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到五代竟然這麼沒用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.27,0:21:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,俗話說宿醉要用酒來治啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.44,0:21:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是沒出息,沒出息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.58,0:21:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起,我實在太沒用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.72,0:21:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別這麼說,是他們太…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.79,0:21:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.93,0:21:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行李箱和土產…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.26,0:21:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼續喝到下一班新幹線來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.84,0:22:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有你跟在身邊\N怎麼還會發生這種事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.71,0:22:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去接你奶奶\N結果只看到行李箱跟土產
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.38,0:22:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本看不到奶奶\N害我擔心得要命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.82,0:22:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶平安抵達了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.99,0:22:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我換奶奶跟你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.75,0:22:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裕作,我忘了告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.96,0:22:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員配你實在太浪費了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.33,0:22:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.16,0:22:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是你千萬不能放棄喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.73,0:22:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你爺爺也曾經熱烈追求過我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.43,0:22:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死纏活纏也會有用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.90,0:22:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.90,0:22:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有,我有拜託公寓的各位\N好好照顧你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.31,0:22:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還給了他們酒錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.84,0:22:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裕作,你有沒有在聽?喂!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.98,0:22:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊,難怪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.85,0:22:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盡情的喝,盡情的喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.65,0:22:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代怎麼還不回來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.45,0:22:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主角不在,場子實在熱不起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.46,0:22:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是又不能不喝,酒錢都拿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.50,0:23:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感覺有沒有好一點?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.03,0:23:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.20,0:23:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些人真是夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.37,0:23:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不介意的話,到我的房間休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.48,0:23:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.88,0:23:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的\N明天你也要出去找工作吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.55,0:23:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不早點躺下來休息的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.25,0:23:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,躺下來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.75,0:23:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,不是,我想請你喝杯茶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.09,0:23:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.29,0:23:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我…那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.86,0:23:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.41,0:23:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?八神的爸爸?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.48,0:23:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,聽說他是人事部長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.32,0:23:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是個大好機會耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.05,0:23:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是你最想進的公司,不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.72,0:23:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒本事的話,一定要靠人脈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.92,0:23:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.56,0:24:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「仲夏夜之夢?\N五代就要找到工作了?」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.09,0:24:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始巴結對方了是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.78,0:24:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩人坐在黎明的護欄上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:34.26,0:24:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至今一直在尋找遺落愛的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.98,0:24:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼…現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:54.18,0:24:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳…一陣風…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.58,0:25:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目光交會…只有…再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.72,0:25:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼…現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:07.79,0:25:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…在雨中…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:11.20,0:25:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忽然…胸口…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:14.50,0:25:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夢…濡濕而發光

